caption.text: Hitting shelves throughout SoCal next week: MONSTERS' PARK, our hulking, cantankerous 12% ABV imperial stout. Sporting a huge roast/chocolate profile, this beer is as aggressive as it is complex, offering layer after layer of robust malt flavor & aroma. Brewing this much Monsters' Park was a gigantic pain in the ass, but it's our way of saying THANK YOU to all the awesome bottle shops, liquor stores, & markets that have done so much to support us. Cheers!

caption.text: Today has been so, so gorgeous. It's days like this that make us so grateful to live and brew in Southern California. Hope everyone has a blast tonight & drinks some super dank beers!
